242
00:14:22,040 --> 00:14:25,940
<i>I think that's where, 2012,
it made me a lot hungrier.</i>

243
00:14:25,980 --> 00:14:28,400
<i>I realized how much I wanted it afterwards</i>

244
00:14:28,440 --> 00:14:32,120
