259
00:15:27,780 --> 00:15:29,300
[press] Alex!

260
00:15:29,340 --> 00:15:30,340
[indistinct chatter]

261
00:15:31,640 --> 00:15:33,276
[Alexander] <i>And there's a big atmosphere.</i>

262
00:15:33,300 --> 00:15:35,580
[all cheering]

263
00:15:36,360 --> 00:15:39,240
