301
00:17:57,720 --> 00:17:58,720
<i>Oh, no.</i>

302
00:18:00,320 --> 00:18:01,220
Oh, wow.

303
00:18:01,260 --> 00:18:03,280
[indistinct chatter]

304
00:18:04,720 --> 00:18:06,400
