305
00:18:08,760 --> 00:18:10,240
Jeez, I hope that kid's good.

306
00:18:11,080 --> 00:18:12,400
Okay, um...

307
00:18:13,040 --> 00:18:14,040
Wow.

308
00:18:15,920 --> 00:18:16,940
