00:18:55,640 --> 00:18:57,860
<i>who were involved in the crash.</i>

324
00:19:00,600 --> 00:19:02,360
I've never seen an accident that bad.

325
00:19:04,600 --> 00:19:06,220
[Alex Jacques] <i>We have a red flag</i>

