333
00:19:49,200 --> 00:19:50,400
<i>at the Belgian Grand Prix.</i>

334
00:19:50,440 --> 00:19:51,956
[newsreader 3] <i>...shocked and saddened,</i>

335
00:19:51,980 --> 00:19:55,020
