368
00:22:27,000 --> 00:22:28,760
<i>I was racing against him,</i>

369
00:22:28,800 --> 00:22:30,920
<i>but at the same time supporting each other</i>

370
00:22:30,960 --> 00:22:33,120
<i>and really motivating each other.</i>

371
00:22:34,120 --> 00:22:38,920
<i>From 13 till 18,
