372
00:22:38,960 --> 00:22:41,580
<i>slept in the same room,
went to the same classes,</i>

373
00:22:41,620 --> 00:22:44,240
<i>trained every single afternoon together.</i>

374
00:22:45,400 --> 00:22:49,360
<i>I knew he wanted as much as I wanted,
