375
00:22:51,120 --> 00:22:51,980
<i>Yeah, it's just...</i>

376
00:22:52,020 --> 00:22:54,520
If I think about all these years,

377
00:22:54,560 --> 00:22:59,280
I've been growing
and becoming the person I am today,

378
00:22:59,740 --> 00:23:01,500
uh, partly thanks to him.

